The '''Ninth Circle of Damnation''' was a location in a version of [[Chaos/Legends|Chaos]], sometimes used as an epitaph for a particularly reviled creature.

==Behind the scenes==
The Ninth Circle is likely a reference to [[Wikipedia:Dante Alighieri|Dante's]] [[Wikipedia:The Divine Comedy|''Divine Comedy'']]. The Ninth Circle of Hell, the innermost circle, was reserved for traitors, and was indeed entirely frozen over.

